1
00:00:00,544 --> 00:00:08,644
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,661 --> 00:00:16,898
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,136 --> 00:00:19,127
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,091 --> 00:00:25,857
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:25,929 --> 00:00:29,296
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,499 --> 00:00:33,060
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,436 --> 00:00:36,803
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:36,873 --> 00:00:44,302
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,380 --> 00:00:53,516
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,590 --> 00:01:01,622
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:01,865 --> 00:01:08,703
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,771 --> 00:01:16,837
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,146 --> 00:01:25,611
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,688 --> 00:01:27,713
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:32,506 --> 00:01:35,839
Sensei!
Please stop this match right away!

16
00:01:45,019 --> 00:01:47,146
There's nothing to worry about...

17
00:01:47,354 --> 00:01:48,116
What?

18
00:01:53,027 --> 00:01:54,392
Sasuke and I...

19
00:01:56,363 --> 00:01:58,763
We didn't just get here late
for no reason.

20
00:02:07,574 --> 00:02:13,535
<i>Late for the Show, But Ready to Go!</i>
<i>The Ultimate Secret Technique is Born!</i>

21
00:02:17,951 --> 00:02:19,213
<i>The third eye...</i>

22
00:02:20,154 --> 00:02:22,622
<i>There is no doubt... That Jutsu is...!</i>

23
00:02:23,257 --> 00:02:25,589
Darn... Gaara...

24
00:02:26,393 --> 00:02:30,762
Tora, Saru, Ne, Tatsu, Tori,
Inu, Ne...

25
00:02:31,131 --> 00:02:36,000
Mi, Inu, Uma, Ushi, Tora, U, Tori...

26
00:02:36,070 --> 00:02:40,439
Tatsu, Mi, Inu, Ne, Tora, Ushi, Saru...

27
00:02:43,310 --> 00:02:45,278
Tatsu, Mi, Hitsuji, Saru...

28
00:02:45,913 --> 00:02:47,938
Tori, Saru, I, Hitsuji, Uma...

29
00:02:48,282 --> 00:02:50,546
Tatsu, Tora...

30
00:02:53,353 --> 00:02:55,548
Tora, Saru, Ushi, Hitsuji, Ne, Uma...

31
00:02:57,091 --> 00:03:00,618
Tora, Ushi, Ne, Tora, Tatsu...

32
00:03:01,361 --> 00:03:03,795
Tori, Tatsu, Mi...

33
00:03:07,101 --> 00:03:08,693
Hitsuji, Saru, Tori...

34
00:03:10,370 --> 00:03:14,636
Tatsu, Tora, Hitsuji, Saru, Tori...

35
00:03:15,008 --> 00:03:16,407
<i>As I thought, it's no good.</i>

36
00:03:16,477 --> 00:03:20,971
I, Hitsuji, Uma, Tatsu, Tatsu,
Tatsu, Ushi, Ne...

37
00:03:21,615 --> 00:03:24,846
Inu, I, Tori, Saru, Hitsuji, Uma...

38
00:03:26,253 --> 00:03:27,777
<i>Withdrawing like that...</i>

39
00:03:29,490 --> 00:03:31,481
<i>I don't know what you're up to...</i>

40
00:03:32,759 --> 00:03:34,056
<i>but the timing is perfect.</i>

41
00:03:36,530 --> 00:03:39,727
<i>This thing of mine also takes time!</i>

42
00:04:05,259 --> 00:04:06,886
Hey, is something the matter?

43
00:04:07,861 --> 00:04:08,657
No...

44
00:04:18,605 --> 00:04:19,629
It must be my imagination...

45
00:04:20,807 --> 00:04:21,603
Hurry up!

46
00:04:44,031 --> 00:04:44,725
Sensei...

47
00:04:44,932 --> 00:04:45,694
Hm?

48
00:04:46,433 --> 00:04:49,766
What did you mean when you said
that you didn't get here late for nothing

49
00:04:50,704 --> 00:04:52,296
Hmm...

50
00:04:53,340 --> 00:04:54,068
You want to know why?

51
00:04:54,174 --> 00:04:57,371
Like I said, this isn't the time
to be talking about that!

52
00:04:58,011 --> 00:04:59,410
Shut up and watch him.

53
00:05:06,286 --> 00:05:07,913
'Cause you'll get a real surprise.

54
00:05:27,140 --> 00:05:27,970
<i>That idiot...</i>

55
00:05:28,675 --> 00:05:33,578
<i>Gaara...we never know when</i>
<i>the signal is going to come!</i>

56
00:05:35,148 --> 00:05:38,049
<i>Yeah...</i>
<i>I'm gonna tear him open.</i>

57
00:05:39,987 --> 00:05:42,717
<i>That's how it comes out.</i>
<i>What?</i>

58
00:05:43,557 --> 00:05:45,115
<i>The contents...</i>

59
00:05:45,792 --> 00:05:48,317
<i>Lots and lots are coming out, right?</i>

60
00:05:50,130 --> 00:05:51,961
<i>I'll give it all to you.</i>

61
00:05:53,900 --> 00:05:56,528
<i>I'm always a good boy!</i>

62
00:05:58,005 --> 00:05:59,336
<i>Yeah, let's do it.</i>

63
00:06:00,340 --> 00:06:03,776
<i>Mother, I'm watching so...</i>

64
00:06:07,147 --> 00:06:10,548
Darn! He's totally useless,
no matter what we do now.

65
00:06:11,752 --> 00:06:13,151
He's not even
abiding by the plan.

66
00:06:13,220 --> 00:06:14,983
He looks like he's just going
to screw things up!

67
00:06:15,322 --> 00:06:16,619
That Gaara!

68
00:06:18,425 --> 00:06:22,088
<i>Hey, hey, wouldn't it</i>
<i>be better if we flee...?</i>

69
00:06:26,767 --> 00:06:27,665
Plan?

70
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:41,411
How's it going?

71
00:06:41,782 --> 00:06:44,717
All preparations are proceeding
in accordance with the timeline.

72
00:06:45,952 --> 00:06:48,477
Please hurry up with preparation
for Summoning.

73
00:06:48,689 --> 00:06:50,919
I want to be sure we're able to
make our move at any time.

74
00:06:51,358 --> 00:06:52,086
Understood!

75
00:06:52,959 --> 00:06:55,257
All right, I'll leave that to you.

76
00:07:32,499 --> 00:07:34,023
D-Don't tell me that...

77
00:07:35,435 --> 00:07:38,268
The reason I decided to
train Sasuke was...

78
00:07:40,207 --> 00:07:43,938
because he was like me.

79
00:08:00,193 --> 00:08:01,854
A physical Activation?!

80
00:08:02,696 --> 00:08:03,560
I see...

81
00:08:03,997 --> 00:08:05,988
That's why he went through
the physical training

82
00:08:06,366 --> 00:08:08,766
and increased his speed significantly...!

83
00:08:10,103 --> 00:08:10,762
That's right!

84
00:08:16,643 --> 00:08:17,405
Awesome...

85
00:08:18,011 --> 00:08:19,911
The Chakra is clearly visible
to the naked eye...

86
00:08:20,514 --> 00:08:22,072
What in the world is happening?!

87
00:08:23,950 --> 00:08:25,383
<i>Don't tell me that</i>
<i>he learned that Jutsu...!</i>

88
00:08:27,721 --> 00:08:29,712
<i>So this is the Uchiha Clan...</i>

89
00:08:37,431 --> 00:08:38,659
Exactly...

90
00:08:39,366 --> 00:08:41,732
W-What the heck is that?!

91
00:08:42,702 --> 00:08:45,364
What a sound!
What's that technique?

92
00:08:46,139 --> 00:08:47,299
That's just a jab...

93
00:08:47,874 --> 00:08:48,602
Huh?!

94
00:08:50,010 --> 00:08:53,036
However, it is the one used by
Leaf Villages! number one technician.

95
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:56,841
That's the only original technique
of the Copy Ninja, Kakashi...

96
00:08:58,685 --> 00:09:01,449
It's the special technique used
only for assassinations...

97
00:09:02,255 --> 00:09:04,553
Its secret is in the speed of the jab,

98
00:09:04,791 --> 00:09:07,555
and also the physical aptitude
that gives forth a gigantic Chakra,

99
00:09:08,295 --> 00:09:11,059
the ability of the Chakra to
focus solely on the target,

100
00:09:11,364 --> 00:09:15,266
and moreover the speed of
the jab makes a chichichichichi sound...

101
00:09:15,335 --> 00:09:19,863
A unique sound attack similar
to the rumbling of a thousand birds.

102
00:09:29,983 --> 00:09:33,077
And that's why that technique is called...

103
00:09:39,626 --> 00:09:40,718
Chidori: One Thousand Birds!

104
00:10:16,297 --> 00:10:20,131
No way!
That Gaara's absolute protection is...

105
00:10:21,202 --> 00:10:22,169
It's impossible...

106
00:10:23,637 --> 00:10:24,729
Don't tell me...

107
00:10:27,775 --> 00:10:29,265
Excellent work!...

108
00:10:31,345 --> 00:10:32,175
That's...

109
00:10:33,280 --> 00:10:34,247
Kakashi's...

110
00:10:36,450 --> 00:10:39,442
Chidori...
Also known as Lightning Blade.

111
00:10:41,121 --> 00:10:42,019
Lightning Blade?

112
00:10:43,290 --> 00:10:46,418
Lightning Blade is another name
for the Jutsu derived

113
00:10:46,493 --> 00:10:49,860
from Kakashi's ability to cut through
lightning using that technique.

114
00:10:50,598 --> 00:10:52,725
<i>Huh? Cut through lightning?</i>

115
00:10:53,567 --> 00:10:56,866
<i>Huh? That sounds fishy...</i>

116
00:10:57,238 --> 00:10:58,830
<i>A-Awesome...</i>

117
00:10:59,273 --> 00:11:02,071
The real name of that technique
is Chidori...

118
00:11:02,910 --> 00:11:07,347
The secret is the speed of his jab
that surpasses any human limitations

119
00:11:07,882 --> 00:11:10,146
and the intensity of
the Chakra on his arm...

120
00:11:11,151 --> 00:11:14,712
And that arm turns virtually
into the equivalent of the swing

121
00:11:14,788 --> 00:11:17,188
of a celebrated sword that
cuts through everything.

122
00:11:19,126 --> 00:11:21,754
But what a reckless technique...

123
00:11:22,296 --> 00:11:23,888
That's not for you to say...

124
00:11:24,531 --> 00:11:25,896
Right, Lee?

125
00:11:27,201 --> 00:11:30,864
It's beyond my scope of
comprehension, but...

126
00:11:31,939 --> 00:11:33,167
What an awesome technique!

127
00:11:37,344 --> 00:11:38,641
<i>I can understand it...</i>

128
00:11:39,780 --> 00:11:42,715
<i>If it were me, if I made</i>
<i>a running start at that speed,</i>

129
00:11:42,783 --> 00:11:45,809
<i>I wouldn't make a direct jab attack</i>
<i>on the opponent...</i>

130
00:11:46,553 --> 00:11:48,544
<i>Or rather, I couldn't.</i>

131
00:11:50,724 --> 00:11:52,214
<i>For an opponent,</i>

132
00:11:52,293 --> 00:11:55,126
<i>a straight line attack just gives him</i>
<i>an easy chance to launch a counterblow.</i>

133
00:11:55,796 --> 00:12:00,824
<i>And moreover, I don't have the eyes</i>
<i>to read that counterblow.</i>

134
00:12:03,604 --> 00:12:06,596
<i>I envy you...Sasuke!</i>

135
00:12:08,008 --> 00:12:12,069
<i>When I fought you once, I said...</i>

136
00:12:13,047 --> 00:12:14,537
<i>Even if one understands visually,</i>

137
00:12:14,615 --> 00:12:16,981
<i>it's meaningless unless</i>
<i>one can move physically...</i>

138
00:12:17,985 --> 00:12:19,577
<i>I was filled with</i>
<i>a feeling of superiority.</i>

139
00:12:21,055 --> 00:12:25,583
<i>But now, you have a body that moves</i>
<i>at the same high speed as mine.</i>

140
00:12:28,295 --> 00:12:29,853
<i>Moreover, you have...</i>

141
00:12:31,832 --> 00:12:33,060
<i>the Sharingan!</i>

142
00:12:34,635 --> 00:12:35,795
I caught you!

143
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:42,572
Third Squadron.
We are ready any time.

144
00:12:44,044 --> 00:12:46,308
All preparations are complete
on this end too.

145
00:12:47,348 --> 00:12:49,908
<i>Roger. Proceed with action</i>
<i>at the signal.</i>

146
00:13:00,761 --> 00:13:01,819
Looks like it's almost time.

147
00:13:10,104 --> 00:13:12,902
<i>The guy who was worrying about</i>
<i>Sasuke until just a moment ago...</i>

148
00:13:16,276 --> 00:13:18,574
<i>is now jealous of him.</i>

149
00:13:23,584 --> 00:13:24,642
Sasuke...

150
00:13:27,855 --> 00:13:29,152
<i>This is the feeling!</i>

151
00:13:32,559 --> 00:13:34,254
<i>Summoning Jutsu!</i>

152
00:13:48,242 --> 00:13:50,005
<i>I've gotten stronger...</i>

153
00:13:50,544 --> 00:13:51,909
<i>In order to become Hokage...</i>

154
00:13:51,979 --> 00:13:53,708
<i>In order not to lose to anyone...</i>

155
00:13:55,416 --> 00:13:56,314
<i>Sasuke!</i>

156
00:13:56,650 --> 00:13:58,584
<i>In order not to lose to you.</i>

157
00:14:00,487 --> 00:14:04,548
<i>I want...to fight you, too.</i>

158
00:14:06,160 --> 00:14:08,025
<i>But you are...</i>

159
00:14:09,963 --> 00:14:10,657
<i>Yeah...</i>

160
00:14:30,584 --> 00:14:33,883
What...? This warm thing...?

161
00:14:35,255 --> 00:14:38,520
Mother...? What is...?

162
00:14:50,337 --> 00:14:54,706
Blood... my blood is...!

163
00:14:55,776 --> 00:14:57,038
D-Don't tell me that...

164
00:15:09,590 --> 00:15:12,354
<i>D-Don't tell me that</i>
<i>Gaara is hurt?!</i>

165
00:15:22,035 --> 00:15:22,865
What is it?!

166
00:15:23,837 --> 00:15:25,236
<i>It's that thing's arm!</i>

167
00:15:33,347 --> 00:15:35,838
Darn! Doing something
careless like that...

168
00:15:41,188 --> 00:15:42,917
Has the Perfect Possession happened?

169
00:15:43,323 --> 00:15:46,520
I don't know.
He seems to be injured...

170
00:15:46,727 --> 00:15:48,160
This has never happened before.

171
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:55,361
<i>It gives me the chills</i>
<i>just to remember...</i>

172
00:15:56,036 --> 00:15:59,870
<i>When I first saw that thing,</i>
<i>I wasn't able to eat...</i>

173
00:16:01,375 --> 00:16:04,435
<i>I mean, visually it's totally...</i>

174
00:16:46,954 --> 00:16:48,012
<i>What is...</i>

175
00:16:48,989 --> 00:16:50,354
<i>this sensation?</i>

176
00:17:29,463 --> 00:17:30,953
He's hurt, after all...

177
00:17:32,032 --> 00:17:34,125
The shell was broken when
his body was incomplete!

178
00:17:44,745 --> 00:17:47,179
<i>It's different! Those aren't the eyes!</i>

179
00:17:48,081 --> 00:17:50,675
<i>W-What was that...</i>
<i>that look earlier on?!</i>

180
00:18:31,958 --> 00:18:32,549
Huh?

181
00:18:45,505 --> 00:18:50,169
What's this...? I can't see...

182
00:18:50,811 --> 00:18:52,278
Kakashi! This must be!

183
00:18:52,446 --> 00:18:54,141
Yeah... a Genjutsu!

184
00:18:55,916 --> 00:18:56,814
- Release!
- Release!

185
00:19:09,896 --> 00:19:12,626
What's going on...?

186
00:19:14,101 --> 00:19:14,863
Release!

187
00:19:15,869 --> 00:19:19,771
<i>Genjutsu!</i>
<i>Is Kabuto already moving?</i>

188
00:19:21,108 --> 00:19:23,406
<i>In that case, it's just about time...</i>

189
00:19:28,815 --> 00:19:29,509
<i>It's coming!</i>

190
00:20:03,784 --> 00:20:04,682
<i>Shall we begin?!</i>

191
00:20:18,265 --> 00:20:19,197
It's the signal!

192
00:20:48,829 --> 00:20:50,228
- <i>Start the operation!</i>
- <i>Start the operation!</i>

193
00:21:05,779 --> 00:21:15,848
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

194
00:21:16,290 --> 00:21:27,133
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

195
00:21:37,244 --> 00:21:42,876
<i>Yes, breathe in the air</i>
<i>Lift your face to the sky and jump</i>

196
00:21:42,950 --> 00:21:47,910
<i>If it rains, take a break</i>
<i>Go where the wind takes you</i>

197
00:21:48,288 --> 00:21:53,191
<i>So many regrets</i>
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>

198
00:21:53,260 --> 00:21:58,391
<i>Let's go carve the badges in our chest</i>
<i>Yes, it's Show Time, life begins now.</i>

199
00:21:58,465 --> 00:22:08,636
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

200
00:22:08,942 --> 00:22:19,375
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

201
00:22:19,453 --> 00:22:30,022
<i>Transform sadness into the wind</i>
<i>and continue to forge on</i>

202
00:22:30,097 --> 00:22:35,660
<i>Forge on strong</i>

203
00:22:46,081 --> 00:22:52,020
It got dark all of a sudden...
it feels so good.

204
00:22:52,420 --> 00:22:54,149
I hear something in the distance.

205
00:22:54,222 --> 00:22:57,316
Sakura's voice, Kakashi Sensei's voice...

206
00:22:57,726 --> 00:23:00,024
Scream? I just heard something loud.

207
00:23:00,362 --> 00:23:02,796
I think I do, but...
Sasuke...

208
00:23:02,964 --> 00:23:04,295
I got to watch his match!

209
00:23:04,799 --> 00:23:08,064
But I really don't know
what's going on.

210
00:23:08,770 --> 00:23:10,761
Next time: "Zero Hour!
The Destruction of
the Hidden Leaf Village Begins!"

211
00:23:11,940 --> 00:23:13,908
What in the world is going on?!
